Dialogue: 0,-1:59:38.61,-1:59:40.37,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Success! Integrity! Evidence and its impact!
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:40.37,-1:59:42.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An endless drive to become the best!
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:42.04,-1:59:43.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The year gets off to an unwelcome start.
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:43.61,-1:59:46.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A case turns up as Ran gets a heart-shocking love letter!
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:46.71,-1:59:48.31,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:48.31,-1:59:50.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:50.04,-1:59:51.93,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear? Kitada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} from Class C got dumped again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran! Going home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sonoko! Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about cooking something good for Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. He hasn't been eating any dinner lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A beautiful young schoolgirl like you shouldn't be thinking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:01:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzuki, you could learn something from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll head home too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get my bag, so wait for me by the shoe lockers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:24.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'd better open it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To Ran Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S.H.?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Ran, it's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it in my shoes locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just rip it open already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Please forgive me for sending you this letter so suddenly.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Whenever I'm thinking about you, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}, I can feel my heart beating. I can't even sleep at night.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I would like to meet you.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I'll be waiting for you tomorrow after school, at the fountain in Beika Park.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congrats, Ran! It's a love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he called you 'Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}', he has to be a first-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know you already have Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with Shin'ichi—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh!{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't even have a simple conversation here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you got a love letter?\NI haven't had any in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, it's the first time you got one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're always with Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, so nobody sends you any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you this has nothing to do with Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he a former {\i1}kendō{\i0} club member?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, he's holding a {\i1}shinai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But never mind that, focus on the love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll go, right? To Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'll do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to think about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll go and turn him down in a snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll say you already have a husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't act like it's somebody else's problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}do{\i0} look worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess there's no choice. Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll turn him down for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to turn down?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's four-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look weird, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! She got her very first love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love letter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Oh, my beloved Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I'll hold you close and place a loving kiss on your sweet lips...'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's lying, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't say anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you really {\i1}did{\i0} get a love letter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're interested, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid, why would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I {\i1}am{\i0} a bit interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a first-year student with the initials 'S. H.'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A first-year student?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants to meet her tomorrow at the fountain in Beika Park after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran doesn't know how to handle it, so I'm going to go and turn him down instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:59.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez. And I can't do anything. Who could've sent it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:03.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What should I do? Can I really\Njust leave it to Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's mine if he's handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If something's bothering you, you can talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her father's the great detective Kogorō Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:42.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her husband's the high school detective Shin'ichi Kudō.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know Detective Mouri, and the high-school detective Kudō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to be a Teitan High student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're second-year students.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:07:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should talk about it with you, like that boy suggested...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can, right, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you don't mind speaking to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll help you, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in! Sorry for the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died one year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stayed in the hospital for six months and fought hard, but he couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, it seems someone broke into my house while I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went for a walk with Yūto for two hours at around 1 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I must've forgotten to lock that window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, I usually personally hand the rent to the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I withdrew some money from the bank this morning and put it in this envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it seems the money I had in here was taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taken out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was put back. All the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how do you know it was taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because the money was folded even though you got new notes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly. It's a very faint fold though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I always leave my diary here too, but it looks like someone's been reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The best proof is that someone burnt an incense stick there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was still burning when you arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much of the stick was left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was about half.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the incense stick was lit about 15 minutes before you got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, incense sticks usually last about half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know a lot, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This brat always knows strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone really broke into this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is who broke in and why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He read the diary, so isn't he a stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But except for that diary, it didn't look like anything had been looked through or taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though a thief wouldn't bring the money back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:38.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's hard to imagine a thief lighting up an incense stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt a little bit uncomfortable, so I asked a policeman to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but since nothing was taken,\Nthere wasn't anything to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:49.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The incense stick...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:51.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's the most intriguing part.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:56.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is the culprit one of her acquaintances, or one of her husband's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:10:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, how did you meet your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's really a curious brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a classmate of mine in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we had no feelings for each other back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After graduating from university, we happened to meet each other in the city and started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's not like Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:21.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, you said someone read your diary, but what was written in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things like 'working and taking care of a child everyday is tough,'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'but I get some strength when I think about him.' Childish stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be really hard being alone, Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I already thought about committing suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I have a child, and thought about my late husband who struggled so hard with his illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:11:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it's not just my husband. There are so many people who want to live but can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it'd be unforgivable for me to give up my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's so sad, I'm shedding tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:21.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe the culprit felt the same way we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If that's true, our culprit would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I saw on TV that a thief broke into a house and left without stealing anything after changing his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was the house of a teacher who'd been kind to him when he was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he broke in without knowing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}, you wouldn't happen to be a school teacher, would—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even if you weren't their teacher, you could be somebody they know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More to the point, you could be somebody special to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should write a diary, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:12:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they read said special person's diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A diary that shows so clearly that you're living honestly despite many misfortunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! That's why they didn't take anything and instead just lit an incense stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he even sent you a love letter during high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop joking, Sonoko! We're being serious here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm serious too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I {\i1}did{\i0} get a love letter once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The January of my third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if it hadn't been for that letter,\NI wouldn't even know his name or face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd never been in the same class at all, from first year to third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But apparently he'd always been admiring me, and I just didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The king of one-sided love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The letter said he wanted to meet me at the fountain in Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:12:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hesitated, but I went to tell him my true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I'm glad you have those feelings for me,'
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'but I can't think of anything other than the entrance exams right now.'
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing that, he just left without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shūhei Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! This man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}, were you part of the {\i1}kendō{\i0} club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was the manager during my 2nd year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought. That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, he's the one who broke into your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}, have you heard from him since you graduated?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, about two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From one of my husband's friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never spoke about him to my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he came up in conversation as one of the many other classmates we had at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:31.90,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He did his best, but he couldn't enter the university he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:35.61,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And after graduating, he only found a job in a company he didn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:40.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In the end, he quit that company, and it seems he's doing part-time jobs now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}, by any chance did you enter a top university just after high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'd call it a top university, but I {\i1}did{\i0} enter the university I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it. I saw through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to hear my deduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh geez, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After meeting Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r} at the Beika Park fountain, Shūhei Nagai didn't forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But feeling inferior to her, who'd entered a top university just after high-school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he couldn't bring himself to contact her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, after graduation, as his professional life wasn't any good either,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he ended up without money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As he was already familiar with Beika District, he chose it to commit his theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he was headed to a rich mansion, probably mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and on the way there, he noticed the window in your house was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He figured out the house was empty, and he...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The woman in the photo was the one he'd fallen in love with in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also remembered the man with her as a high school classmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And from the picture on the altar, he realised that the classmate in question had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while he knew it was wrong, he also read the diary he'd found.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He found out about how you were doing your best to live on with your son,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and thought about his classmate who died in his 20s.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he started feeling ashamed of himself, as he was taking advantage of people despite still being healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I see Ran put so much effort into her karate practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sometimes think I should work hard too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Shūhei Nagai decided to redeem himself, and so he put the money back in the envelope,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,burnt a stick in honour of his late classmate, and left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, as he knew he would never come back to this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he went to see the school he graduated from one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that just happened to be when the {\i1}kendō{\i0} club was practising.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, he remembered Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r} and started reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might be staring at the fountain in Beika Park now even!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:22.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was almost the same as what I deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This Nagai guy who I saw in front of the gymnasium seemed a little bit different than you deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looked rather languished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I still don't know why he was carrying a {\i1}shinai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A {\i1}shinai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, was there anything else written in the diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's actually something I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:18:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About 10 days ago, I was involved in a small accident with a man riding a bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, he said everything was OK,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he came back later saying he couldn't turn his head any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told him that I'd pay for his medical fees,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he asked for a 'relationship' instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite persistently, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seemed like a pretty bad guy, so I was afraid something might happen to my son if I'd rejected him too harshly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I didn't tell anybody about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was he today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's on a business trip until tonight, and I don't think he was today's intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, everything you just told us was written in your diary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this Nagai guy was carrying a {\i1}shinai{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you that girl's boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And keep your hands off her kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What are you blabbering?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had enough yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you sayin'? I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who the hell are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:20:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you couldn't turn your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You despicable monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister, it seems you can't turn your neck for real now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I read your diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I wanted to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,11 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,11 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so glad you'd come to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind. I'll go there by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still don't know what I'll say, but I have to tell him how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I owe him my sincerity for having written that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.51,0:23:00.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:05.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:11.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran said she wanted to tell him the truth, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:13.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did she mean about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I'd wait for you, but you ended up being the one waiting for me, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:28.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.97,0:23:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a big fan of you, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}, the captain of the karate club!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.19,0:23:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Thanks.{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep doing your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.34,0:23:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a first-year boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko! And Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here I thought I was gonna hear Ran's true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.01,0:23:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.96,0:23:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're able to grasp women's hearts too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.24,0:23:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.91,0:24:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A girl who looks like Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.70,0:24:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did she get involved in some sort of case?
